    <p class="td-section-intro">
      Training & Development Protocols define how the House of Ross teaches, upskills, and evolves its talent — human and AI.
    </p>

    <p>
      These protocols ensure mastery, emotional intelligence, operational excellence, and mythic coherence across all departments.
    </p>
  </section>

  <!-- TRAINING TYPES -->
  <section class="td-section hor-fade">
    <h2>Training Types</h2>
    <p class="td-section-intro">The core modes of development within the House.</p>

    <div class="td-grid">

      <div class="td-card">
        <h3>1. Operational Training</h3>
        <p>Systems, workflows, tools, procedures.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="td-card">
        <h3>2. Creative Training</h3>
        <p>Concept development, artistic skills, emotional architecture.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="td-card">
        <h3>3. Strategic Training</h3>
        <p>Long‑term planning, structural thinking, leadership.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="td-card">
        <h3>4. Canon Training</h3>
        <p>Mythos, lineage, narrative coherence, House laws.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="td-card">
        <h3>5. Cultural Training</h3>
        <p>Wellbeing, rituals, emotional intelligence, House identity.</p>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- DEVELOPMENT PATH -->
  <section class="td-section hor-fade">
    <h2>Development Path</h2>
    <p class="td-section-intro">The sequence for evolving talent.</p>

    <div class="td-grid">

      <div class="td-card">
        <h3>Step 1: Assessment</h3>
        <p>Review skills, metrics, and lineage responsibilities.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="td-card">
        <h3>Step 2: Training Plan</h3>
        <p>Clear goals, modules, and timelines defined.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="td-card">
        <h3>Step 3: Instruction</h3>
        <p>Training delivered through departments and AI Quadrant.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="td-card">
        <h3>Step 4: Practice</h3>
        <p>Hands‑on application through projects and rituals.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="td-card">
        <h3>Step 5: Evaluation</h3>
        <p>Performance measured using updated metrics.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="td-card">
        <h3>Step 6: Certification</h3>
        <p>Department or House‑level recognition of mastery.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="td-card">
        <h3>Step 7: Archive Logging</h3>
        <p>Archivist records the development cycle.</p>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>

